{"lastModified":1775138718410,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::89dc73d0-f5a1-11ee-9704-8351e4f9c0b7","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nDiscover the perfect blend of comfort and style aboard the Topaz, a 56ft catamaran designed for the ultimate cruising experience. With spacious outdoor areas including a flybridge sunbathing area, aft cockpit dining, and a large swim platform, you’ll enjoy breathtaking views and seamless outdoor living. \nInside, the open-plan saloon with panoramic windows invites natural light, while the 4 luxurious double cabins and 1 bunk bed cabin with en-suite bathrooms ensure complete privacy and relaxation. Energy-efficient features, including solar panels and a water maker, allow for self-sufficient cruising.\nFrom water toys like paddleboards and snorkeling gear to high-speed Wi-Fi and premium amenities, every detail is designed for your comfort. Your professional crew of three will ensure a tailored, five-star experience, making the LAG 560 Topaz your perfect yacht escape.\n\nKey Features:\n- Expansive flybridge with sunbathing area \n- Hydraulic bathing platform and underwater lights\n- Hydraulic gangway - 8x120W solar panels for o-grid cruising \n- Full water toy collection including paddleboards and inflatable beds \n- High-speed Wi-Fi, premium toiletries, and a fully - equipped galley \n\nThe name Topaz evokes the brilliance and clarity of the precious gemstone, symbolizing elegance, luxury, and radiant beauty. Known for its vibrant hues, Topaz reflects the sparkling waters and unforgettable experiences aboard this exceptional yacht.","blueprint":{"name":"TOPAZ","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::89dc73d0-f5a1-11ee-9704-8351e4f9c0b7::assets::0c276260-fdcf-11ef-9c73-8738e259cd0b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89dc73d0-f5a1-11ee-9704-8351e4f9c0b7::assets::0c219600-fdcf-11ef-9294-91d0916ab24d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89dc73d0-f5a1-11ee-9704-8351e4f9